    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>A very simple implementation with <a href=\"http://docs.oracle.com/javase/6/docs/api/java/lang/String.html#split(java.lang.String)\" rel=\"noreferrer\"><code>String.split()</code></a>:</p>\n\n<pre><code>String path = \"/abc/def/ghfj.doc\";\n// Split path into segments\nString segments[] = path.split(\"/\");\n// Grab the last segment\nString document = segments[segments.length - 1];\n</code></pre>\n"
