    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>Another way is to use <a href=\"https://commons.apache.org/proper/commons-lang/apidocs/org/apache/commons/lang3/StringUtils.html#substringAfterLast-java.lang.String-java.lang.String-\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"><code>StringUtils.substringAfterLast()</code></a> from Apache Commons Lang:</p>\n<pre><code>String path = &quot;/abc/def/ghfj.doc&quot;\nString fileName = StringUtils.substringAfterLast(path, &quot;/&quot;);\n</code></pre>\n<p>If you pass null to this method, it will return null.<br />\nIf there is no match with <em>separator</em>, it will return empty string.</p>\n"
