    "body" : "<p>With <a href=\"https://mvnrepository.com/artifact/com.google.guava/guava/23.6-jre\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">Guava</a> do this:</p>\n\n<pre><code>String id=\"/abc/def/ghfj.doc\";\nString valIfSplitIsEmpty=\"\";\nreturn Iterables.getLast(Splitter.on(\"/\").split(id),valIfSplitIsEmpty);\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>Eventually configure the <code>Splitter</code> and use</p>\n\n<pre><code>Splitter.on(\"/\")\n.trimResults()\n.omitEmptyStrings()\n...\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>Also take a look into <a href=\"https://github.com/google/guava/wiki/StringsExplained#splitter\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">this article on guava Splitter</a> and <a href=\"https://github.com/google/guava/wiki/CollectionUtilitiesExplained#iterables\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">this article on guava Iterables</a></p>\n"
